   +-RELEASE.iNFORMATION

       Eons before the Green Lantern Corps, the Guardians of the Universe
       created an android race of interstellar policeùthe Manhunters. When
       corrupted programming made them punish all life, the Manhunters were
       exiled. Now they've returned, seeking vengeance. You are Hal Jordan,
       the first human Green Lantern, armed with a power ring charged by
       your will. Green Lantern: Rise of the Manhunters features the
       likeness and voice talent of Ryan Reynolds.

